  <div class="eyebrow">About</div>
  <h1>Chaos is my fuel. Ambiguity is my playground.</h1>
  <p class="lead" style="max-width: 680px;">
    I'm a technical product leader who has spent 16+ years bridging engineering and the business,
    with a PhD in Systems Engineering underneath the product instincts. I've been building with AI
    and LLMs since 2014, back when it was still an unusual thing to say out loud in a product meeting.
  </p>
